data.description: Serenity awaits! Tucked in the trees sits a lovely 1,126sqft home on 2.55 acres with shared private Rogue River access/boat ramp.  This cutie is a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a 3 car attached garage/shop area! Open floor plan, spacious kitchen, wood top island, knotty pine cabinets, dining area and large living room with woodstove (currently used as shelving) Bay window/sitting area looking out to front yard. Primary bedroom ensuite with sliding glass door to back yard. Give the covered patio area some TLC and could be an awesome outdoor kitchen! New chain-link fencing around front and side yard. Land is level around home with hills for privacy. 15 minutes to shopping and restaurants!
